<!DOCTYPE html><html> <head>  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initialscale=1.0" />  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />  <style type="text/css">@media screen and (max-width: 480px) {slot[style] {margin-right: 0 !important;}.columnDiv {margin-right: 0 !important;}}@media screen and (min-width: 480px) {slot[style] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}.columnDiv {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}}</style>  <style type="text/css">@media screen and (max-width: 480px) {.contentbuilderBaseColumnRow .columnCell {display:inline-block;width:100%}}</style>  <style type="text/css">.contentpageDefaultEmailTemplatePageTemplate .contentRoot {width: 600px;}@media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {.contentpageDefaultEmailTemplatePageTemplate .contentRoot {width: 320px;}}</style> </head> <body>  <table class="contentpageDefaultEmailTemplatePageTemplate" style="background-color: #E9EAEC;" role="presentation" id="contentpage_emailTemplateBodyContent" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">       <tr>     <td width="100%" align="center">      <table class="contentRoot" style="background-color: #FFFFFF;" role="presentation" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">               <tr>         <td style="padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">          <table class="contentbuilderBaseColumnRow" style="background-color:;" role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">                       <tr valign="top">             <td width="100%" class="columnCell" style="vertical-align: top;display: inline-block">              <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; word-break:break-word;">                               <tr>                 <td>                  <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; word-break: break-word; font-size: 14px" id="contentRegion" role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" locked="0">                                       <tr>                     <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><u><b>Order Summary</b></u><br /><br /> Order Date:&nbsp;{{{SBQQ__Quote__c.NATT_Final_Approval_Date__c}}}<br /><br /> Order Status:&nbsp;{{{SBQQ__Quote__c.NATT_Status_Fx__c}}}<br /><br /> Dealer Name:&nbsp;{{{SBQQ__Quote__c.SBQQ__Account__c}}}<br /><br /> End Customer:&nbsp;{{{SBQQ__Quote__c.NATT_End_Customer__c}}}<br /><br /> Data Plan:<br /> {{{SBQQ__Quote__c.NATT_eSolutions_Plans_For_Email__c}}}<br /><br /> Welcome to the Carrier® Transicold® Lynx Fleet™ telematics service! An order has been placed on your behalf by your authorized Carrier Transicold Dealer or another Carrier representative.<br /><br /> That order and your use of Carrier Transicold's Lynx Fleet equipment and/or service is subject to all terms and conditions contained in the Lynx Fleet Terms and Conditions of Use (https://tta.lynxfleet.carrier.com/sensornet/html5/iapp/login/html/terms.html) and the Lynx Fleet Privacy and Data Usage Notice (https://tta.lynxfleet.carrier.com/sensornet/html5/iapp/login/html/privacy.html) found by clicking on the links above.<br /><br /> To complete your Lynx Fleet order you MUST REPLY ALL to this email, type "CONFIRM" in the subject line, and send it to Carrier Transicold at esolutions@carrier.com. That acknowledgment will ensure your awareness and confirm your acceptance of all terms and conditions contained in these documents, which govern your firm's use of the Carrier Transicold Lynx Fleet service. YOUR LYNX FLEET ORDER CANNOT BE FINALIZED UNITL THIS STEP IS COMPLETE. Please keep a copy of this email for your records.</td>                    </tr>                                     </table></td>                </tr>                             </table></td>            </tr>                     </table></td>        </tr>             </table></td>    </tr>     </table> </body></html>